{"tid":884751,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"去過清境 合歡山 花蓮既巴打請進 有行程求教","createTime":"2018-11-01T00:25:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T10:07:57.000Z","uid":32786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9e437526a3506605b243a8690de8cf9d96212dc9","tid":884751,"uid":32786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T00:25:30.000Z","msg":"背景資料 我同女朋友 兩人 平時都多行山既<br />\n目的: 睇日出 行下山<br />\n下年會去台中<br />\n咁就想去清境 合歡山 花蓮<br />\n上網GOOGLE過(以前去過一兩次台中 大概知點搭車個D)<br />\n台中干城(8:20)- 清境(10:40)-合歡山(12:XX)<br />\n***中午12點到合歡山是否會好悶冇野做? 行幾個鐘山大唔大問題?<br />\n其實我最想問 <br />\n1 . 如果住係合歡山上面 係咪好易對高山症有反應 如果真係有高山症 可以買藥去減低個症狀?<br />\n2. 訂松雪樓 / 隔離唔知咩山莊 有咩注意 (好大機會都係訂隔離山莊床鋪)<br />\n3.合歡山落花蓮既車 只有梨山 &gt; 花蓮 係15:54 經大禹嶺(花蓮客運) &lt; 我見由合歡人係可以行山行到去大禹嶺 ,會唔會上唔到車好多人?<br />\n4.花蓮景點 大多都係要包車去 先睇得多 是嗎?<br />\n最後..其實係咪住清境好D,住合歡山是否不智?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不勝感激"},{"pid":"c2dc69f7914c6477558fd0a7d8fc4639574fd971","tid":884751,"uid":32786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T01:47:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1e5afa770adc17bc67320d16629e04a49c2d2c8","tid":884751,"uid":134806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e437526a3506605b243a8690de8cf9d96212dc9","tid":884751,"uid":32786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T00:25:30.000Z","msg":"背景資料 我同女朋友 兩人 平時都多行山既<br />\n目的: 睇日出 行下山<br />\n下年會去台中<br />\n咁就想去清境 合歡山 花蓮<br />\n上網GOOGLE過(以前去過一兩次台中 大概知點搭車個D)<br />\n台中干城(8:20)- 清境(10:40)-合歡山(12:XX)<br />\n***中午12點到合歡山是否會好悶冇野做? 行幾個鐘山大唔大問題?<br />\n其實我最想問 <br />\n1 . 如果住係合歡山上面 係咪好易對高山症有反應 如果真係有高山症 可以買藥去減低個症狀?<br />\n2. 訂松雪樓 / 隔離唔知咩山莊 有咩注意 (好大機會都係訂隔離山莊床鋪)<br />\n3.合歡山落花蓮既車 只有梨山 &gt; 花蓮 係15:54 經大禹嶺(花蓮客運) &lt; 我見由合歡人係可以行山行到去大禹嶺 ,會唔會上唔到車好多人?<br />\n4.花蓮景點 大多都係要包車去 先睇得多 是嗎?<br />\n最後..其實係咪住清境好D,住合歡山是否不智?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不勝感激"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:05:05.000Z","msg":"月中去完答你，半日行山夠晒，有沒有高山反應睇個人，眼見好多遊客都無反應"},{"pid":"092af4ffbc529b3fecc3b246853f5f74df4041f0","tid":884751,"uid":58958,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:17:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02f64977010485019cb781b8f395fa36f1f4c96f","tid":884751,"uid":58958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:17:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"17fe414de923289a68759ba51c1f03ecaa918857","tid":884751,"uid":32786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"092af4ffbc529b3fecc3b246853f5f74df4041f0","tid":884751,"uid":58958,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:17:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:37:38.000Z","msg":"我見一泊兩食 3450 兩個人都可以既<br />\n清境好似都差唔多價錢?<br />\n<br />\n了解 多謝巴打意見"},{"pid":"82e7cb6d9c513ec59a2148ee2fa811d52cd826c3","tid":884751,"uid":32786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1e5afa770adc17bc67320d16629e04a49c2d2c8","tid":884751,"uid":134806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"p